    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Purely animal or physical part of human nature; the senses and appetites of the physical body.  Also, gratification of the senses, self-indulgence, or the quality of being lascivious.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
